        <section id="detailed_desc" deliveryTarget="details" otherprops="no-title">
            <p></p>
        </section>
        <section id="restriction" deliveryTarget="details">
            <title>使用限制</title>
            <p>无。</p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters" deliveryTarget="details">
            <title>参数</title>
            <parml>
            <plentry props="cpp">
                <pt props="cpp">uid</pt>
                <pd props="cpp">远端用户或主播的用户 ID。当其离开频道或掉线时触发该回调。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry props="cpp">
                <pt props="cpp">state</pt>
                <pd props="cpp">远端视频状态。详见 <xref keyref="REMOTE_VIDEO_STATE"/>。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry props="cpp">
                <pt props="cpp">reason</pt>
                <pd props="cpp">远端视频状态变化的原因。详见 <xref keyref="REMOTE_VIDEO_STATE_REASON"/>。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry props="cpp">
                <pt props="cpp">elapsed</pt>
                <pd props="cpp">从本地客户端调用 <codeph>joinChannel</codeph> 到该回调被触发的时间（毫秒）。</pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
        <section id="return_values" props="bp electron flutter rn unity unreal">
            <title><ph keyref="return-section-title"/></title>
        <p props="flutter">方法成功调用时，无返回值；方法调用失败时，会抛出 <xref keyref="AgoraRtcException"/> 异常，你需要捕获异常并进行处理。</p>
        <ul props="android apple bp electron rn unity unreal">
                <li>0: 方法调用成功。</li>
